# webdev-poe

### Pages Included:
- **Home** (index.html) - Welcome and featured products
- **About** (about.html) - Company story and team
- **Shop** (products.html) - Product catalog with images
- **Contact** (contact.html) - Contact form and information
- **Enquiries** (enquiry.html) - Customer enquiry form
- **Reviews** (reviews.html) - Customer review form


### JavaScript Enhancements:
- Form validation with error messages
- Interactive accordions (FAQ sections)
- Modal windows (map viewer)
- Lightbox image gallery
- Search and filter functionality
- Smooth animations and transitions

### SEO Optimization:
- Meta tags and descriptions
- Proper header hierarchy (H1-H3)
- Image alt text optimization
- Mobile-friendly design
- robots.txt and sitemap.xml
